high_descs: Turn left and go to the white table
Grab an apple off of the table
Turn around and go to the fridge
Cool the apple in the fridge and then take it out
Turn right and go to the white table
Put the apple on the table
anns.task_desc: Putting a cold apple on the white table

high_descs: Turn around the face the round white table.
Pick up the closest red apple from the round white table.
Turn left, then hang another left to walk towards the fridge.
Chill the apple in the fridge, removing it afterwards.
Turn left to walk back towards the round white table.
Put the red apple down on the round white table.
anns.task_desc: Chill a red apple from the round white table in the fridge, putting it back on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and face the table
Pick up the closest apple from the table
Cross the kitchen and walk to the front of the refrigerator
Open the refrigerator door, put the apple on the shelf inside, close the refrigerator, open the refrigerator, take the apple out, and close the refrigerator door.
Turn around and cross the kitchen to the table
Put the apple on the table
anns.task_desc: Chill an apple in the refrigerator and put it on the table
